rows.name:
Unable to pinpoint source of interference.
We can't tell what's happening, sir.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33170100_MSG0030
rows.name: Any word from the raiding party?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33170100_MSG0050
rows.name: Maybe they're just unable to reach us.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33170100_MSG0060
rows.name: Keep hailing them from our side.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33170100_MSG0080
rows.name: We will just have to trust in their abilities.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33170100_MSG0110
rows.name: Just a surprise to hear you sound so...positive.[ST:wait ]
